OL,5,G2305 Murder Scene: The Incident Room
OL,6,     FIn Swindon, 60-year-old Tom Rogers
OL,7,     Fwas brutally stabbed by a
OL,8,     Fstranger. Investigators must piece
OL,9,     Ftogether every shred of evidence
OL,10,     Fto see whether the same killer has
OL,11,     Fattacked before.
OL,12,G0005 Britain's Most Dangerous Prisoners
OL,13,     FJames O'Rourke's reputation has
OL,14,     Fmade him one of the UK's most
OL,15,     Ffeared prisoners. He's attacked
OL,16,     Fprison officers, even holding some
OL,17,     Fhostage, and in 2022 murdered a
OL,18,     Ffellow inmate.
